<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <%- include('./partials/head', {title: "Website: Return Policy"}); %>
    </head>
    <header>
        <%- include('./partials/header'); %>
    </header>
    <body class="bg-light">
        <div class="container mt-5">
            <h1 class="mb-4">Other Issues with Login</h1>
    
            <div class="accordion" id="loginIssuesAccordion">
                <!-- Question 1 -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            What should I do if I forgot my password?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#loginIssuesAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            If you've forgotten your password, use the "Forgot Password" link on the login page. You'll be prompted to enter your email address. Follow the instructions sent to your email to reset your password.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <!-- Question 2 -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            What if my account is locked?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#loginIssuesAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            If your account is locked due to multiple unsuccessful login attempts, wait for a few minutes and try again. If the problem persists, contact customer support for assistance with unlocking your account.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <!-- Question 3 -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            Why am I seeing an "Invalid Username or Password" error?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#loginIssuesAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            This error typically means that the username or password you entered is incorrect. Double-check your credentials for typos and ensure that your Caps Lock key is not enabled. If youâ€™re sure your information is correct, try resetting your password.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <!-- Question 4 -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                            How can I troubleshoot login issues on mobile devices?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#loginIssuesAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            If you're having trouble logging in on a mobile device, first ensure that your app or browser is up to date. Clear the app cache or browser cookies and try logging in again. If issues persist, try restarting your device or accessing the login page from a different browser or device.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <!-- Question 5 -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                            What should I do if I receive a "Server Error" during login?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#loginIssuesAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            A "Server Error" during login typically indicates an issue with the server rather than with your credentials. Check the service status page for any ongoing issues or maintenance. If the problem persists, contact support for further assistance.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>